00:00:54.210 --> 00:00:58.189
iCal version 1 was basically a product
that was a geared up personal calendar.

00:00:58.189 --> 00:00:59.780
And so you can kind of get that.

00:00:59.780 --> 00:01:07.840
It started out as a download that you could get
for Tiger, and it actually shifted with that system

00:01:07.840 --> 00:01:10.909
