00:37:59.869 --> 00:38:03.659
And we certainly believe with the--
Snow Leopard Calendaring solutions

00:38:03.659 --> 00:38:06.099
that we've gone a long way to addressing those requirements.

00:38:06.099 --> 00:38:08.110
