00:47:11.860 --> 00:47:15.740
and it's not shared with all the other attendees
so you can explain why it is you can't come

00:47:15.739 --> 00:47:19.739
to a meeting or any other comments you have about it.

00:47:19.739 --> 00:47:23.549
iCal supports now-- supports Exchange like the iPhone does.

00:47:23.550 --> 00:47:31.289
It's got a much simpler experience for setting up your
